
                          Movie Trailer

  What is it?
  -----------

  The Movie Trailer project is a web page that users can see different
  trailers of movies. If a user wants to add a new movie he/she can 
  simply create a new instance in entertainment_center.py and add the
  descriptions of the new movie there. Then open the fresh_tomatoes.html
  in a browser and voalla the new trailer is added in the web page.


  Installation
  ------------
  
  Just clone the project and open the html file in your browser.
